overview: THE HUNDRED BUCKS is an upcoming Bollywood film. Which is directed by Dushyant Pratap Singh And Produced by Rajnish Ram Puri, Sandeep Puri, Vibhav Tomar, Pratima Totla & Ritu Singh . The main cast of the film will feature actors like Kavita Tripathi, Dinesh Bawara, Zaid Shaikh & Rajesh Mishra. The film will be released in Indian cinemas on 21 February 2020 by Jai Viratra Entertainment Limited
title: The Hundred Bucks
